      "x": 2840,
      "y": 245,
      "width": 230.39999999999998,
      "height": 28,
      "text": "What if instead:",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-16",
      "x": 2840,
      "y": 290,
      "width": 421.2,
      "height": 154,
      "text": "\u2022 Source of truth IS the config source\n\u2022 AI understands protocol semantics\n\u2022 Natural language drives the workflow\n\u2022 Every action is audited automatically\n\u2022 Validation is built into every change\n\n   Intent in  \u2192  Working network out",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
