      "y": 285,
      "width": 230.39999999999998,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "\u2713 OSPF neighbors FULL\n\u2713 BGP Established\n\u2713 All 6 loopbacks in RIB\n\u2713 Route propagation OK",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
