      "y": 345,
      "width": 218.4,
      "height": 54,
      "text": "\u2022 FULL adjacency with P2\n\u2022 Learns complete LSDB\n\u2022 Discovers all router-IDs",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
