      "x": 14840,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 1080,
      "name": "Scene 8 \u2014 Safety and Audit",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-197",
      "x": 14940,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 720.0,
      "height": 52,
      "text": "Trust Through Constraints",
      "fontSize": 48,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-198",
      "x": 14940,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 24,
      "text": "How NetClaw earns production access",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#868e96"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "el-199",
      "x": 14920,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 380,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff5f5",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "strokeWidth": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-200",
      "x": 14940,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 356.4,
      "height": 26,
      "text": "Non-Negotiable Safety Rules",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-201",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 576.0,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Never guess device state \u2014 always run a show command first",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-202",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 290,
      "width": 480.0,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Never apply config without a pre-change baseline",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-203",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 595.1999999999999,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Never run destructive commands (write erase, reload, format)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-204",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 390,
      "width": 614.4,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Never skip the Change Request \u2014 ServiceNow CR must be Approved",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-205",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 604.8,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Always verify after changes \u2014 if verification fails, escalate",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-206",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 490,
      "width": 585.6,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "\u2716 Always commit to GAIT \u2014 immutable audit trail every session",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "el-207",
      "x": 15790,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#dee2e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "strokeWidth": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-208",
      "x": 15810,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 369.59999999999997,
      "height": 26,
      "text": "GAIT \u2014 Git-based AI Tracking",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#495057"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-209",
      "x": 15810,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 468.0,
      "height": 152,
      "text": "Every session records:\n\u2022 What was asked\n\u2022 What data was collected (and from where)\n\u2022 What was changed (and on what device)\n\u2022 What the verification result was\n\u2022 What tickets were created\n\n\u2192 \"What did the AI do and why?\" always has an answer",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "el-210",
      "x": 15790,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#862e9c",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f0fc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "strokeWidth": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-211",
      "x": 15810,
      "y": 435,
      "width": 528.0,
      "height": 24,
      "text": "DefenseClaw \u2014 Enterprise Security (Optional)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#862e9c"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-212",
      "x": 15810,
      "y": 475,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 108,
      "text": "Ring 1: NVIDIA OpenShell (container isolation)\nRing 2: Cisco DefenseClaw (runtime guardrails)\nRing 3: NetClaw agent (constrained by both)\n\nLLM inspection \u2022 Tool call filtering \u2022 SIEM export\nSecret exfiltration prevention \u2022 Audit logging",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "el-213",
      "x": 14920,
      "y": 680,
      "width": 1560,
      "height": 100,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "strokeWidth": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-214",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 1036.8,
      "height": 28,
      "text": "Production-Grade AI Automation = Capability + Constraints + Auditability",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "el-215",
      "x": 14960,
      "y": 740,
      "width": 787.1999999999999,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "The agent CAN do powerful things. The safety model ensures it does them CORRECTLY.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#495057"
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
